quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  39,8,"Ne Omundu nanyoola amasila kosikosi asaba Nyasaye wuwe namukalushila, ne namuhelesia tsimbabaasi okhurula ewuwe yebilila akayasabanga imbeli mana natsokasia Nyasaye nende Abanyasaye bandi mbu kho akosie Abandu khu injila yiye, wikhoye nende obukhayi bubwo hatiti, toto ewe oli mubaandu bomumulilo"
  39,9,"Koo ulia ulaamanga eshilo Nyasaye wuwe niyeema niyenama mana naba noburi khu inyanga imalilishi, ne nasuubila okhunyoola tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye wuwe. Boola mbu:“ bakhaba nashilala abamanyile nende abalamanyile tawe, toto abachesi nibobetsulilanga.’’"
  39,10,"Boola enywe Abasumba banje basuubila, murie Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi, balia bakhola amalayi khushialo khuno balinyoola amalayi, ne eshialo shia Nyasaye neshiyaangufu, toto abesumilisi balihebwa omurungo kwabu okhubura eshichelo"
  39,11,"Boola mbu: “esie ndalomesibwa okhulaama Nyasaye mubutswenufu"
  39,12,Ne ndalomesibwa okhuba weyimbeli mubasalamu
  39,13,"Boola mbu: “ esie eritsaanga eshinyasio shie inyanga ikhongo nekhaya okhuloonda ka Nyasaye Omulesi wanje.”"
  39,14,Ni Nyasaye butswa wenaamanga nemutswenushila
  39,15,"Kho lame shia mwenya owulali Ye. Boola mbu: “toto balia abatiba mana nibatibia emioyo chiabu inyanga yeyindukho,” koo manye mbu, okho nikho okhutiba khwa habulafu"
  39,16,"Baliba nende ebichelo biomulilo biawukhane hekulu nende hasi wabu, endio nilwa Nyasaye arisia Abandu bebe, enywe abasumba banje muurie"
  39,17,"Ne balia basita ehale khubulaami bwobukori mana nibamukalushila Nyasaye, basuubisibwa obulayi imbeli wa Nyasaye , subisia Abasumba banje"
  39,18,"Balia bawulilanga likhuwa mana nibaloonda lilia lilayi lialio, abo nibo ba Nyasaye yalunjisia, ne abo nibo bamachesi"
  39,19,"Ne ulia okhoyeshele okhunyoola omurungo kweshinyasio, ewe olinobunyali bwokhuhabina uli mumulilo"
  39,20,"Halali balia baria Nyasaye wabu balinyoola tsigorofa ebikoro biombakhwa hekulu webindi, emialo chiburanga hasi wabio, indache ya Nyasaye ne Nyasaye shanyala okhwima shiayakhulaka tawe"
  39,21,"Koo shololangakhwo shinga Nyasaye yeshinjia amaatsi okhurula mwikulu, mana nakabusia mutsindoto mwiloba, mana namesilia emimela chikabukhane obukondo, mana chiume chikalukhane chibe namabuyu, mana achikhole amasakaria , toto mu ako khulimwo nende eshitsulisio khubandu bamachesi"
  39,22,"Koo ulia wa Nyasaye yafungula eshilifu shishie khubuisilamu, mana naba mubulafu bururulanga ewa Nyasaye Omulesi ( bakhaba nashilala nende ulia womwoyo omumu?) eshinyasio eshikhongo shili khubemioyo emiumu chaletsulilanga Nyasaye, abo bali mubukori obwa habulafu"
  39,23,"Nyasaye yeshia amakhuwa amalayi muno , eshitabu shietsinyaali tsifwanana tsiakalushilwa, tsirenjinjia emibili chia balia abaria Nyasaye wabu Omulesi, mana nitsikololosia emibili chiabu nende emioyo chiabu khukhwitsulila Nyasaye, obo nibo obulunjifu bwa Nyasaye alunjisinjia khubwo owayenya, ne owa Nyasaye alekha abulaho umulunjisia"
  39,24,"Koo ulia wo bweni bubwe bulibukanana nende eshinyasio eshibii inyanga yeyindukho (aliba nashilala nende abalayi?) mana ababii baliboolelwa mbu: “ pile kalia kamwakholanga.”"
  39,25,Bakhaya balia abali imbeli wabu mana eshinyasio nishibetsela munjila yabalamanyile tawe
  39,26,"Mana Nyasaye nabakhofia eshinyasio shiobuteshele, ne eshinyasio shieyinyanga yeyindukho neshikhongo muno, bamanyanga khwo"
  39,27,Ne toto khwachelasilia Abandu mu Kurani ino buli imbia yamachelasio kho banyoole okhwitsulila
  39,28,Ikurani yolwarabu ibulamwo tsingatsio khobanyoole okhuria Nyasaye
  39,29,"Nyasaye achelasia Omundu uli nende Abaami bakholelanga halala basolananga, nende Omundu uli nende Omwami mulala, koo bakhaba nashilala? Oluyali lwoosi nilwa Nyasaye, halali obunji bwabu shibamanyile tawe"
  39,30,Toto ewe olifwa nabo boosi balifwa
  39,31,"Mana toto enywe imbeli wa Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi mulisoolana, inyanga yeyindukho"